statements: SELECT id, user_id, fingerprint_data, scan_timestamp FROM biometric_data WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM biometric_data WHERE user_id = 10 ORDER BY scan_timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, user_id FROM biometric_data WHERE scan_timestamp < '2023-01-01' AND user_id BETWEEN 5 AND 10;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_scans FROM biometric_data GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_scans FROM biometric_data WHERE scan_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2023-01-01' GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY total_scans DESC;
SELECT id, user_id, scan_timestamp FROM biometric_data WHERE user_id = 1;

SELECT u.username, r.role_id FROM users u JOIN user_roles ur ON u.user_id = ur.user_id JOIN roles r ON ur.role_id = r.role_id;
